## Stack Actual (MVP en Producción)

```
Next.js 15       App Router, RSC, ISR
React 19         UI
TypeScript       Strict mode siempre
Tailwind CSS 4   Solo clases utilitarias, no CSS custom salvo globals.css
Framer Motion    Animaciones — no over-engineer
Vercel           Hosting + CI/CD (push to main = deploy)
Resend           Email / newsletter
GitHub           Version control
```

